body_html: @andrehentz I built for my Mac desktop and it worked no problem. So I started from scratch and rebuilt for Android again, re-deployed, and it worked! (?!?) No idea how I got into whatever state I was in, but it seems to be working now. Sorry for the false alarm, and thanks again for the explanation about running multiple times. I'll close this now and reopen if I can ever find a repro.
